---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Lythaus — the human-first publishing platform."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <section class="section">
    <h1>About Lythaus</h1>
    <p>
      Lythaus is a calm, invite-only space for authentic voices. We believe
      publishing should amplify thoughtful ideas — not reward noise.
    </p>
    <h2>Our principles</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Human-first moderation</strong> — AI flags, humans decide.</li>
      <li><strong>Invite-only growth</strong> — quality over quantity.</li>
      <li><strong>Transparent ranking</strong> — no hidden algorithms.</li>
      <li><strong>Privacy by default</strong> — minimal data, maximum control.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>The team</h2>
    <p>
      Lythaus is built by a small team passionate about creating healthier
      online spaces. We are based in South Africa and building for the world.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Lythaus — a human-first publishing platform."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <section class="section">
    <h1>About Lythaus</h1>
    <p>
      Lythaus is a publishing platform focused on authentic human content.
      The platform is built around transparent moderation, community-driven
      appeals, and a reputation system that rewards constructive participation.
    </p>
    <p>
      The name reflects the mission: a clear space for real voices.
    </p>
    <h2>Principles</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Human-first content — AI-generated posts are not publishable.</li>
      <li>Transparent moderation — every decision is logged and appealable.</li>
      <li>Community accountability — members participate in the appeals process.</li>
      <li>Privacy by default — data export and deletion are built in.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
